---
---
<div class="panel sb-panel novel-workshop-panel">
  <div class="novel-hero">
    <div class="novel-hero-badge">NOVEL LORE WORKSHOP</div>
    <div class="novel-hero-main">
      <div class="novel-hero-copy">
        <h2>📚 小说世界书工坊</h2>
        <p>把长篇小说整理成可控的世界书包，同时生成真正用于管理解锁状态的 MVU 变量。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="novel-hero-orbit">
        <span class="novel-orbit-ring"></span>
        <span class="novel-orbit-core">MVU</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  <div class="novel-stats" id="novelStatsBar">
      <span class="novel-stat-chip">等待导入文本</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="novel-card novel-import-dock">
    <div class="novel-card-head">
      <strong>原始资料</strong>
      <span>先导入小说，再配置门控</span>
    </div>
    <div class="novel-card-body">
      <label id="novelDropzone" class="novel-dropzone" for="novelSourceFile">
        <span class="novel-dropzone-icon">📥</span>
        <span class="novel-dropzone-title">点击或拖拽导入小说文件</span>
        <span class="novel-dropzone-subtitle">全文只在内存里参与生成，不会直接渲染到输入框，适合 txt / md / json</span>
      </label>
      <div class="novel-upload-row">
        <label class="novel-upload-btn" for="novelSourceFile">选择文件</label>
        <input id="novelSourceFile" type="file" accept=".txt,.md,.json" style="display:none;" />
        <span id="novelFileHint" class="novel-upload-hint">支持 txt / md / json</span>
        <button id="btnNovelClearFile" type="button" class="novel-upload-clear" style="display:none;">清空文件</button>
      </div>
      <div id="novelFileSummary" class="novel-file-summary" style="display:none;"></div>
      <div class="novel-source-layout">
        <div class="novel-editor-block">
          <div class="novel-editor-head">
            <label for="novelSourceText">手动补充摘录</label>
            <span>这里适合补少量片段、章节摘要或人工备注，不再直接显示整本小说全文。</span>
          </div>
          <textarea id="novelSourceText" class="novel-textarea novel-source-text" placeholder="贴入章节原文、人物设定表、卷纲摘要，或已经切片过的知识抽取结果。"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="novel-editor-block">
          <div class="novel-editor-head">
            <label for="novelContextText">补充说明</label>
            <span>告诉 AI 这次抽取应该避开什么、重点抓什么</span>
          </div>
          <textarea id="novelContextText" class="novel-textarea novel-context-text" placeholder="例如：只做公开信息；不要提前泄露真相；优先抽人物、地点、势力；这是卷一到卷三的资料。"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="novel-card novel-pipeline-card">
    <div class="novel-card-head">
      <strong>处理步骤</strong>
      <span>生成前先看预估调用次数</span>
    </div>
    <div class="novel-card-body">
      <div id="novelEstimateBar" class="novel-estimate-bar"></div>
      <div id="novelWorkflowSteps" class="novel-workflow-steps"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="novel-grid">

    <section class="novel-card novel-config-card">
      <div class="novel-card-head">
        <strong>门控设计</strong>
        <span>世界书 + 变量联动</span>
      </div>
      <div class="novel-card-body">
        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>门控模式</label>
            <select id="novelGateMode">
              <option value="stage_flags">阶段 + 揭露标记</option>
              <option value="stage_only">仅剧情阶段</option>
              <option value="public_only">仅公开资料</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>条目预算</label>
            <input id="novelEntryBudget" type="number" min="1" value="18" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>整理模式</label>
            <select id="novelNarrativeMode">
              <option value="story">按剧情推进</option>
              <option value="lore_only">只做世界观</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>模式说明</label>
            <div id="novelNarrativeHint" class="novel-inline-note">按剧情推进：允许保留阶段性关系变化、关键事件后果和阅读顺序。只做世界观：尽量剥离时间线，只保留稳定设定。</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>单次分片字数</label>
            <select id="novelChunkSize">
              <option value="12000">12,000 字</option>
              <option value="20000" selected>20,000 字</option>
              <option value="32000">32,000 字</option>
              <option value="50000">50,000 字</option>
              <option value="80000">80,000 字</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
            <label>上下文提醒</label>
            <div class="novel-inline-note">模型限制按 token 算，不按字数算。这里是经验字数上限，用来做稳妥分片。</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="novel-focus-wrap">
          <label class="novel-focus-label">抽取重点</label>
          <div id="novelFocusTags" class="novel-focus-tags"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="novel-stage-preview">
          <div class="novel-stage-preview-head">
            <span>默认解锁路径</span>
            <strong>公开 → 前期 → 中期 → 后期 → 终局</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="novel-stage-preview-track">
            <span>公开</span>
            <span>前期</span>
            <span>中期</span>
            <span>后期</span>
            <span>终局</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="novel-action-stack">
          <button id="btnNovelGenerate" class="btn novel-primary-btn">🧬 生成并注入小说世界书</button>
          <button id="btnNovelReset" class="btn novel-secondary-btn">重置工坊</button>
        </div>
        <div id="novelStatusText" class="status-text novel-status-text"></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section id="novelManager" class="novel-manager" style="display:none;">
    <div class="novel-manager-head">
      <div>
        <strong>🧭 世界书解锁管理</strong>
        <p id="novelSummaryText">尚未生成。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="novel-manager-actions">
        <button id="btnNovelSyncVariables" class="btn novel-sync-btn">同步到 MVU 变量节点</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="novel-manager-grid">
      <div class="novel-manager-block">
        <div class="novel-block-title">当前阶段</div>
        <div id="novelStageButtons" class="novel-stage-buttons"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="novel-manager-block">
        <div class="novel-block-title">揭露标记</div>
        <div id="novelFlagList" class="novel-flag-list"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="novel-preview-shell">
      <div class="novel-preview-head">
        <strong>实体索引预览</strong>
        <span id="novelEntityCount">0 个实体</span>
      </div>
      <div id="novelEntityPreview" class="novel-entity-preview"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .novel-workshop-panel {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12), transparent 34%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08), transparent 38%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13, 18, 32, 0.96), rgba(15, 23, 37, 0.94));
  }

  .novel-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 16px 18px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.34), rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.72)),
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12), transparent 24%);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .novel-hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.26);
    background: rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.4);
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  .novel-hero-main {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .novel-hero-copy h2 {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #e0f2fe;
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .novel-hero-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .novel-hero-orbit {
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 78px;
    height: 78px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }

  .novel-orbit-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.26);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.14), inset 0 0 16px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.06);
  }

  .novel-orbit-ring::before,
  .novel-orbit-ring::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.28);
    animation: novel-orbit-spin 14s linear infinite;
  }

  .novel-orbit-ring::after {
    inset: 18px;
    border-color: rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.22);
    animation-direction: reverse;
    animation-duration: 10s;
  }

  @keyframes novel-orbit-spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .novel-orbit-core {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.94), rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.76));
    color: #082f49;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
  }

  .novel-stats {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  .novel-stat-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 26px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.72);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.44);
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .novel-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .novel-import-dock {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .novel-pipeline-card {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .novel-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.64);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.76), rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.58));
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .novel-card-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 11px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.66);
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72);
  }

  .novel-card-head strong {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .novel-card-head span {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: normal;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .novel-card-body {
    padding: 14px;
  }

  .novel-upload-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .novel-dropzone {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    min-height: 138px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 18px 16px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.36);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1), transparent 46%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.26), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.52));
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .novel-dropzone:hover,
  .novel-dropzone.is-dragover {
    border-color: rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.72);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18), transparent 46%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.42), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.68));
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .novel-dropzone-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.24));
  }

  .novel-dropzone-title {
    color: #e0f2fe;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .novel-dropzone-subtitle {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 380px;
  }

  .novel-upload-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 32px;
    padding: 0 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.28);
    background: rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.42);
    color: #7dd3fc;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .novel-upload-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.38);
    color: #e0f2fe;
  }

  .novel-upload-hint {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
  }

  .novel-upload-clear {
    min-height: 32px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.24);
    background: rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.16);
    color: #fca5a5;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .novel-upload-clear:hover {
    background: rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.3);
    color: #fecaca;
  }

  .novel-file-summary {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 12px 13px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.22), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.52));
  }

  .novel-file-summary strong {
    display: block;
    color: #e0f2fe;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .novel-file-summary span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .novel-estimate-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .novel-estimate-card {
    padding: 11px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.7);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.66), rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.4));
  }

  .novel-estimate-card strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .novel-estimate-card span {
    display: block;
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .novel-estimate-card.is-accent {
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.28);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.22), rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.28));
  }

  .novel-workflow-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .novel-workflow-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 34px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 11px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.7);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.34);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .novel-workflow-step.is-active {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.28), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.74));
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .novel-workflow-step.is-done {
    border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.22);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.2), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72));
  }

  .novel-workflow-index {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    background: rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.46);
    color: #7dd3fc;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .novel-workflow-copy strong {
    display: block;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .novel-workflow-copy span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 4px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .novel-textarea {
    min-height: 120px;
    resize: vertical;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.7), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.82));
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16);
  }

  .novel-source-text {
    min-height: 120px;
  }

  .novel-context-text {
    min-height: 110px;
  }

  .novel-source-layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .novel-editor-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .novel-editor-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .novel-editor-head label {
    margin: 0;
    color: #dbeafe;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .novel-editor-head span {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .novel-focus-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .novel-inline-note {
    min-height: 42px;
    padding: 9px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.7);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.28);
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .novel-focus-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .novel-focus-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .novel-focus-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 30px;
    padding: 0 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.74);
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.58);
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .novel-focus-tag:hover {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.34);
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  .novel-focus-tag.active {
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.38);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.34), rgba(12, 74, 110, 0.28));
    color: #fcd34d;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
  }

  .novel-stage-preview {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.18);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.16), rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.12));
  }

  .novel-stage-preview-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  .novel-stage-preview-head strong {
    color: #fef3c7;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  .novel-stage-preview-track {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .novel-stage-preview-track span {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    min-height: 34px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.32);
